    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "1. Construction of Community Training Center 2. Equip Community Training Centre with furniture, office tables, chairs for training hall, kitchen materials, milk chilling vat, solar panels) - support to develop a mechanism for sustainability of community training training 3. Establishing Mini Irrigation Plant - constructing two reservoirs of 40000 liter 4. Improving road (5 km) from the community training center to Sukute 5. Conducting Agriculture Capacity Building Training for Farmers - Agriculture Training on IPM, compost making, vegetable farming, floriculture, improved seeds, support agriculture tools6. Conducting skill development training for young men and women -sewing training, sanitary napkin making training, plumbing training, food processing (jam and jelly making, candy making, potato chips and corn flakes making, cheese making) - Promote microenterprise at the village, - orientation and promotion of agrotourism 7. Promote personal health and hygiene and environment preservation (IEC materials design, publication, dissemination; club formation, awareness raising)"
      },
